{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "马如龙在阳光下与绝大师、冯超凡对峙，拒绝铁震天原先谈成的交易，提出以马如龙一命换铁震天等两命。他逐步暗示自己能找到马如龙，最终坦承自己就是众人寻找的人，并说明容貌已被玉玲珑易容改变，无法恢复本来面目。绝大师和冯超凡反而因这份牺牲毫无理由而不肯相信。铁震天大笑又怒吼，宁愿贬低马如龙也要逼他离开；绝大师却抓住马如龙不走，冷酷逼两人同死。铁震天悲愤斥骂绝大师不是人，力竭仍扑向他。此时墙外飘入带茉莉香的碧绿色浓雾，一名笑声如铃的神秘女子出声打断死局。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "这交易本来很不错，而且已经谈成了，你为什么不答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "listener_name": "铁震天",
      "text": "因为我也要跟他们谈个交易。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "listener_name": "铁震天",
      "text": "我的交易比你的还好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "什么交易？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "还有什么交易比他这交易更好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "他想用他们的两条命，来换我的一条命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "这是亏本生意，我不做。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "你的交易怎么做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "用一条命换他们的两条命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "这交易谈不成。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "没有人能够用一条命换他们这两条命。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "没有人的命这么值钱。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "我知道最少有一个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "马如龙！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "我知道你们最想找的一个人并不是铁震天，而是马如龙。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "绝大师承认。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "用马如龙的一条命来换他们两条命，能不能换得过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "能！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "只可惜谁也找不到马如龙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "有一个人能找得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "最少有一个人能找到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "我！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "只要你放他们走，我保证，能够把马如龙交给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "你是个好朋友，这也是个好交易，只可惜这交易做不成的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "因为谁也不会相信你说的鬼话。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "你应该看得出我说的不是鬼话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "我看得出，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "可是我不能先放他们走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "你信不过我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "只要你交出马如龙，我立刻放人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "我保证。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "listener_name": "冯超凡",
      "text": "你们信不过我，我为什么要相信你们？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "因为我是冯超凡，他是绝大师，你只不过是个来历不明的陌生人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "你要谈成这交易，只有照我们的话做。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "否则我们就先杀铁震天，再杀你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "好，我相信你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "我就是你们要找的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "你就是马如龙？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "我就是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "不为什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "你认不出我，因为我的脸已经被人修整易容过，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "我在这里用杂货店做掩护已经躲了很久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "现在你们是不是已经应该放他们走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "listener_name": "冯超凡",
      "text": "你看怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "你看呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "如果他真是马如龙，他有什么理由要为了铁震天出卖自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "listener_name": "冯超凡",
      "text": "没有理由。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "listener_name": "冯超凡",
      "text": "完全没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "我早就知道你骗不过他们的，我早就知道谁也不会相信你的鬼话。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "你只不过是个来历不明的无名小卒而已，我却是'翻天覆地'的大盗铁震天，就算你有十条命，也换不过我的一条命，你还是快走吧。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "listener_name": "马如龙",
      "text": "你的交易既然谈不成，你为什么还不快走？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "listener_name": "铁震天",
      "text": "因为他是你的朋友，你的朋友都是好朋友。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "listener_name": "铁震天",
      "text": "所以他决心要陪你一起死在这里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "你说过让他走的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "listener_name": "铁震天",
      "text": "我说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "listener_name": "绝大师",
      "text": "现在你是不是又不肯让他走了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
